{"name":"Purify","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Nurgle, the Chaos God of Disease and Decay, is abhorrent to Shallya. This spell allows you to target any one Daemon or follower of Nurgle within 48 yards (24 squares) and overwhelm him with the purifying power of Shallya. This is an anathema to the servants of the Plague Lord. The target of purify loses 1d10 Wounds, regardless of Toughness Bonus or armour, and must make a successful Will Power Test or be stunned for 1 round.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Shallya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":16},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A burning torch","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"oDy5hnRLnJwdGAlP"}
